{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":714,"text":"Hey guys."},{"time":2041,"text":"It's funny, someone just mentioned MacGyver,"},{"time":3811,"text":"because that was, like, I loved it,"},{"time":5751,"text":"and when I was seven, I taped a fork to a drill"},{"time":11071,"text":"and I was like, \"Hey, Mom, I'm going to Olive Garden.\""},{"time":13792,"text":"And -- (Drilling noise) (Laughter)"},{"time":17943,"text":"And it worked really well there."},{"time":20875,"text":"And you know, it had a profound effect on me."},{"time":24696,"text":"It sounds silly, but I thought, okay,"},{"time":26924,"text":"the way the world works can be changed,"},{"time":29796,"text":"and it can be changed by me in these small ways."},{"time":31947,"text":"And my relationship to"},{"time":33661,"text":"especially human-made objects"},{"time":35153,"text":"which someone else said they work like this,"},{"time":37038,"text":"well, I can say they work a different way, a little bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":40188,"text":"And so, about 20 years later,"},{"time":42686,"text":"I didn't realize the full effect of this,"},{"time":44194,"text":"but I went to Costa Rica"},{"time":45971,"text":"and I stayed with these Guaymí natives there,"},{"time":48138,"text":"and they could pull leaves off of trees and make shingles out of them,"},{"time":51640,"text":"and they could make beds out of trees,"},{"time":54809,"text":"and they could -- I watched this woman for three days."},{"time":57043,"text":"I was there. She was peeling this palm frond apart,"},{"time":60290,"text":"these little threads off of it, and she'd roll the threads together"},{"time":63427,"text":"and make little thicker threads, like strings,"},{"time":66145,"text":"and she would weave the strings together,"},{"time":68966,"text":"and as the materiality of this exact very bag"},{"time":72446,"text":"formed before my eyes over those three days,"},{"time":75334,"text":"the materiality of the way the world works,"},{"time":78641,"text":"of reality, kind of started to unravel in my mind,"},{"time":81115,"text":"because I realized that this bag and these clothes"},{"time":84463,"text":"and the trampoline you have at home and the pencil sharpener,"},{"time":86847,"text":"everything you have is made out of either a tree or a rock"},{"time":90980,"text":"or something we dug out of the ground and did some process to,"},{"time":93324,"text":"maybe a more complicated one, but still, everything was made that way."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97235,"text":"And so I had to start studying,"},{"time":99427,"text":"who is it that's making these decisions?"},{"time":101137,"text":"Who's making these things? How did they make them?"},{"time":102946,"text":"What stops us from making them?"},{"time":104440,"text":"Because this is how reality is created."},{"time":107345,"text":"So I started right away. I was at MIT Media Lab,"},{"time":109932,"text":"and I was studying the maker movement"},{"time":112481,"text":"and makers and creativity."},{"time":114031,"text":"And I started in nature, because I saw these Guaymís"},{"time":116158,"text":"doing it in nature, and there just seems to be less barriers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119203,"text":"So I went to Vermont to Not Back to School Camp,"},{"time":122548,"text":"where there's unschoolers who are just kind of hanging out"},{"time":125800,"text":"and willing to try anything."},{"time":127287,"text":"So I said, \"Let's go into the woods near this stream"},{"time":129580,"text":"and just put stuff together, you know, make something,"},{"time":131609,"text":"I don't care, geometrical shapes, just grab some junk from around you."},{"time":134196,"text":"We won't bring anything with us."},{"time":135845,"text":"And, like, within minutes, this is very easy for adults"},{"time":138364,"text":"and teens to do."},{"time":139452,"text":"Here's a triangle that was being formed underneath a flowing stream,"},{"time":142587,"text":"and the shape of an oak leaf being made"},{"time":145171,"text":"by other small oak leaves being put together."},{"time":148365,"text":"A leaf tied to a stick with a blade of grass."},{"time":151102,"text":"The materiality and fleshiness and meat of the mushroom"},{"time":153798,"text":"being explored by how it can hold up different objects being stuck into it."},{"time":157170,"text":"And after about 45 minutes, you get really intricate projects"},{"time":160735,"text":"like leaves sorted by hue, so you get a color fade"},{"time":163962,"text":"and put in a circle like a wreath."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165806,"text":"And the creator of this, he said,"},{"time":168422,"text":"\"This is fire. I call this fire.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":170092,"text":"And someone asked him, \"How do you get those sticks"},{"time":172319,"text":"to stay on that tree?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":174080,"text":"And he's like, \"I don't know, but I can show you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":177190,"text":"And I'm like, \"Wow, that's really amazing."},{"time":178822,"text":"He doesn't know, but he can show you.\""},{"time":180205,"text":"So his hands know and his intuition knows,"},{"time":182785,"text":"but sometimes what we know gets in the way"},{"time":185641,"text":"of what could be, especially"},{"time":187678,"text":"when it comes to the human-made, human-built world."},{"time":190605,"text":"We think we already know how something works,"},{"time":192902,"text":"so we can't imagine how it could work."},{"time":195045,"text":"We know how it's supposed to work,"},{"time":196391,"text":"so we can't suppose all the things that could be possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":199798,"text":"So kids don't have as hard of a time with this,"},{"time":203645,"text":"and I saw in my own son, I gave him this book."},{"time":206930,"text":"I'm a good hippie dad, so I'm like,"},{"time":209138,"text":"\"Okay, you're going to learn to love the moon."},{"time":211315,"text":"I'm going to give you some building blocks"},{"time":213648,"text":"and they're nonrectilinear cactus building blocks,"},{"time":216798,"text":"so it's totally legit.\""},{"time":218612,"text":"But he doesn't really know what to do with these."},{"time":220886,"text":"I didn't show him."},{"time":222458,"text":"And so he's like, \"Okay, I'll just mess around with this.\""},{"time":223966,"text":"This is no different than the sticks are to the teens in the forest."},{"time":227869,"text":"Just going to try to put them in shapes"},{"time":230341,"text":"and push on them and stuff."},{"time":232117,"text":"And before long, he's kind of got this mechanism"},{"time":234781,"text":"where you can almost launch and catapult objects around,"},{"time":238451,"text":"and he enlists us in helping him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":240716,"text":"And at this point, I'm starting to wonder,"},{"time":242651,"text":"what kind of tools can we give people,"},{"time":245452,"text":"especially adults, who know too much,"},{"time":248406,"text":"so that they can see the world as malleable,"},{"time":250697,"text":"so they see themselves as agents of change"},{"time":252174,"text":"in their everyday lives."},{"time":253636,"text":"Because the most advanced scientists are really"},{"time":256122,"text":"just kind of pushing the way the world itself works,"},{"time":258854,"text":"pushing what matter can do,"},{"time":260031,"text":"the most advanced artists are just pushing the medium,"},{"time":262812,"text":"and any sufficiently complicated task,"},{"time":264758,"text":"whether you're a cook or a carpenter or you're raising a child --"},{"time":267683,"text":"anything that's complicated --"},{"time":269369,"text":"comes up with problems that aren't solved in the middle of it,"},{"time":271896,"text":"and you can't do a good job getting it done unless you can say,"},{"time":275222,"text":"\"Okay, well we're just going to have to refigure this."},{"time":277350,"text":"I don't care that pencils are supposed to be for writing."},{"time":280029,"text":"I'm going to use them a different way.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":282214,"text":"So let me show you a little demo."},{"time":287013,"text":"This is a little piano circuit right in here,"},{"time":291575,"text":"and this is an ordinary paintbrush"},{"time":293666,"text":"that I smashed it together with. (Beeping)"},{"time":296661,"text":"And so, with some ketchup,"},{"time":298524,"text":"— (musical notes) —"},{"time":301998,"text":"and then I can kind of"},{"time":303287,"text":"— (musical notes) —"},{"time":309782,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":311741,"text":"And that's awesome, right?"},{"time":314464,"text":"But this is not what's awesome."},{"time":315774,"text":"What's awesome is what happens"},{"time":317336,"text":"when you give the piano circuit to people."},{"time":320755,"text":"A pencil is not just a pencil."},{"time":322138,"text":"Look what it has in the middle of it."},{"time":323806,"text":"That's a wire running down the middle,"},{"time":326558,"text":"and not only is it a wire,"},{"time":327999,"text":"if you take that piano circuit, you can thumbtack"},{"time":330359,"text":"into the middle of a pencil,"},{"time":332298,"text":"and you can lay out wire on the page, too,"},{"time":335218,"text":"and get electrical current to run through it."},{"time":337639,"text":"And so you can kind of hack a pencil,"},{"time":339521,"text":"just by thumbtacking into it with a little piano electrical circuit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":345042,"text":"And the electricity runs through your body too."},{"time":346982,"text":"And then you can take the little piano circuit off the pencil."},{"time":350328,"text":"You can make one of these brushes just on the fly."},{"time":353782,"text":"All you do is connect to the bristles,"},{"time":355589,"text":"and the bristles are wet, so they conduct,"},{"time":357581,"text":"and the person's body conducts,"},{"time":360150,"text":"and leather is great to paint on,"},{"time":362149,"text":"and then you can start hooking to everything,"},{"time":364854,"text":"even the kitchen sink."},{"time":365849,"text":"The metal in the sink is conductive."},{"time":367768,"text":"Flowing water acts like a theremin or a violin."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371321,"text":"(Musical notes)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376303,"text":"And you can even hook to the trees."},{"time":377557,"text":"Anything in the world is either conductive or not conductive,"},{"time":380953,"text":"and you can use those together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382727,"text":"So — (Laughter) —"},{"time":384183,"text":"I took this to those same teens, because those teens are"},{"time":387338,"text":"really awesome, and they'll try things that I won't try."},{"time":389795,"text":"I don't even have access to a facial piercing if I wanted to."},{"time":392778,"text":"And this young woman, she made what she called a hula-looper,"},{"time":396799,"text":"and as the hula hoop traveled around her body,"},{"time":399212,"text":"she has a circuit taped to her shirt right there."},{"time":401983,"text":"You can see her pointing to it in the picture."},{"time":404024,"text":"And every time the hula hoop would smush against her body,"},{"time":406440,"text":"it would connect two little pieces of copper tape,"},{"time":408623,"text":"and it would make a sound, and the next sound,"},{"time":410359,"text":"and it would loop the same sounds over and over again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":412895,"text":"I ran these workshops everywhere."},{"time":414824,"text":"In Taiwan, at an art museum, this 12-year-old girl"},{"time":417834,"text":"made a mushroom organ out of some mushrooms that were from Taiwan"},{"time":421496,"text":"and some electrical tape and hot glue."},{"time":423280,"text":"And professional designers were making artifacts"},{"time":425361,"text":"with this thing strapped onto it."},{"time":427140,"text":"And big companies like Intel"},{"time":429354,"text":"or smaller design firms like Ideo or startups like Bump,"},{"time":433007,"text":"were inviting me to give workshops,"},{"time":434559,"text":"just to practice this idea of smashing electronics"},{"time":436954,"text":"and everyday objects together."},{"time":438786,"text":"And then we came up with this idea"},{"time":441447,"text":"to not just use electronics,"},{"time":443235,"text":"but let's just smash computers with everyday objects"},{"time":446207,"text":"and see how that goes over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":448767,"text":"And so I just want to do a quick demo."},{"time":452366,"text":"So this is the MaKey MaKey circuit,"},{"time":454991,"text":"and I'm just going to set it up from the beginning in front of you."},{"time":457890,"text":"So I'll just plug it in, and now it's on by USB."},{"time":461923,"text":"And I'll just hook up the forward arrow."},{"time":464560,"text":"You guys are facing that way, so I'll hook it to this one."},{"time":468001,"text":"And I'll just hook up a little ground wire to it."},{"time":471647,"text":"And now, if I touch this piece of pizza,"},{"time":474171,"text":"the slides that I showed you before should go forward."},{"time":477235,"text":"And now if I hook up this wire just by connecting it"},{"time":480667,"text":"to the left arrow, I'm kind of programming it by where I hook it up,"},{"time":483939,"text":"now I have a left arrow and a right arrow,"},{"time":486960,"text":"so I should be able to go forwards and backwards"},{"time":489160,"text":"and forwards and backwards. Awesome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":492264,"text":"And so we're like, \"We gotta put a video out about this.\""},{"time":494808,"text":"Because no one really believed that this was important"},{"time":497376,"text":"or meaningful except me and, like, one other guy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500355,"text":"So we made a video to prove that"},{"time":502040,"text":"there's lots of stuff you can do."},{"time":503580,"text":"You can kind of sketch with Play-Doh"},{"time":505612,"text":"and just Google for game controllers."},{"time":509546,"text":"Just ordinary Play-Doh, nothing special."},{"time":512233,"text":"And you can literally draw joysticks"},{"time":513934,"text":"and just find Pacman on your computer and then just hook it up. (Video game noises)"},{"time":521057,"text":"And you know the little plastic drawers you can get at Target?"},{"time":524560,"text":"Well, if you take those out, they hold water great,"},{"time":526768,"text":"but you can totally cut your toes,"},{"time":528904,"text":"so yeah, just be careful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531592,"text":"You know the Happiness Project, where the experts"},{"time":534464,"text":"are setting up the piano stairs, and how cool that is?"},{"time":537222,"text":"Well, I think it's cool,"},{"time":538432,"text":"but we should be doing that stuff ourselves."},{"time":540775,"text":"It shouldn't be a set of experts engineering the way the world works."},{"time":543858,"text":"We should all be participating"},{"time":545833,"text":"in changing the way the world works together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547753,"text":"Aluminum foil. Everybody has a cat."},{"time":549940,"text":"Get a bowl of water. This is just Photo Booth on your Mac OS."},{"time":553124,"text":"Hover the mouse over the \"take a photo\" button,"},{"time":555184,"text":"and you've got a little cat photo booth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":556759,"text":"And so we needed hundreds of people to buy this."},{"time":559448,"text":"If hundreds of people didn't buy this, we couldn't put it on the market."},{"time":562536,"text":"And so we put it up on Kickstarter,"},{"time":565437,"text":"and hundreds of people bought it in the first day."},{"time":568432,"text":"And then 30 days later,"},{"time":569458,"text":"11,000 people had backed the project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":572725,"text":"And then what the best part is, we started getting"},{"time":574840,"text":"a flood of videos in of people doing crazy things with it."},{"time":578912,"text":"So this is \"The Star-Spangled Banner\" by eating lunch,"},{"time":581574,"text":"including drinking Listerine."},{"time":583648,"text":"And we actually sent this guy materials."},{"time":585114,"text":"We're like, \"We're sponsoring you, man."},{"time":586595,"text":"You're, like, a pro maker.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":588705,"text":"Okay, just wait for this one. This is good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592320,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":594139,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597624,"text":"And these guys at the exploratorium are"},{"time":599501,"text":"playing house plants as if they were drums."},{"time":604723,"text":"And dads and daughters are completing circuits in special ways."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608297,"text":"And then this brother -- look at this diagram."},{"time":610649,"text":"See where it says \"sister\"?"},{"time":611937,"text":"I love when people put humans on the diagram."},{"time":614393,"text":"I always add humans to any technical --"},{"time":616861,"text":"if you're drawing a technical diagram, put a human in it."},{"time":618993,"text":"And this kid is so sweet. He made this trampoline slideshow advancer for his sister"},{"time":623463,"text":"so that on her birthday, she could be the star of the show,"},{"time":625536,"text":"jumping on the trampoline to advance the slides."},{"time":628281,"text":"And this guy rounded up his dogs and he made a dog piano."}]},{"cues":[{"time":634134,"text":"And this is fun,"},{"time":636579,"text":"and what could be more useful than feeling alive and fun?"},{"time":639466,"text":"But it's also very serious because"},{"time":641986,"text":"all this accessibility stuff started coming up,"},{"time":644154,"text":"where people can't use computers, necessarily."},{"time":647110,"text":"Like this dad who wrote us, his son has cerebral palsy"},{"time":649802,"text":"and he can't use a normal keyboard."},{"time":651674,"text":"And so his dad couldn't necessarily afford"},{"time":655245,"text":"to buy all these custom controllers."},{"time":657087,"text":"And so, with the MaKey MaKey, he planned to make"},{"time":658713,"text":"these gloves to allow him to navigate the web."},{"time":661607,"text":"And a huge eruption of discussion"},{"time":663767,"text":"around accessibility came, and we're really excited about that."},{"time":666722,"text":"We didn't plan for that at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668623,"text":"And then all these professional musicians started using it,"},{"time":671431,"text":"like at Coachella, just this weekend"},{"time":673559,"text":"Jurassic 5 was using this onstage,"},{"time":676711,"text":"and this D.J. is just from Brooklyn, right around here,"},{"time":680412,"text":"and he put this up last month."},{"time":682423,"text":"And I love the carrot on the turntable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684527,"text":"(Music: Massive Attack — \"Teardrop\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":691355,"text":"Most people cannot play them that way. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":694101,"text":"And when this started to get serious,"},{"time":695523,"text":"I thought, I'd better put a really serious warning label on the box that this comes in,"},{"time":698950,"text":"because otherwise people are going to be getting this"},{"time":700652,"text":"and they're going to be turning into agents of creative change,"},{"time":702891,"text":"and governments will be crumbling,"},{"time":704183,"text":"and I wouldn't have told people, so I thought I'd better warn them."},{"time":706542,"text":"And I also put this little surprise. When you open the lid"},{"time":708871,"text":"of the box, it says, \"The world is a construction kit.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":711731,"text":"And as you start to mess around this way,"},{"time":713578,"text":"I think that, in some small ways, you do start to see"},{"time":716677,"text":"the landscape of your everyday life"},{"time":718729,"text":"a little bit more like something you could express yourself with,"},{"time":721622,"text":"and a little bit more like you could participate"},{"time":723861,"text":"in designing the future of the way the world works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":726325,"text":"And so next time you're on an escalator"},{"time":730113,"text":"and you drop an M&amp;M by accident,"},{"time":731789,"text":"you know, maybe that's an M&amp;M surfboard, not an escalator,"},{"time":734949,"text":"so don't pick it up right away."},{"time":736156,"text":"Maybe take some more stuff out of your pockets"},{"time":738344,"text":"and throw it down, and maybe some chapstick, whatever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741653,"text":"I used to want to design a utopian society"},{"time":746615,"text":"or a perfect world or something like that."},{"time":748987,"text":"But as I'm kind of getting older"},{"time":750441,"text":"and kind of messing with all this stuff,"},{"time":752017,"text":"I'm realizing that my idea of a perfect world"},{"time":754785,"text":"really can't be designed by one person"},{"time":756801,"text":"or even by a million experts."},{"time":758357,"text":"It's really going to be seven billion pairs of hands,"},{"time":761525,"text":"each following their own passions,"},{"time":763933,"text":"and each kind of like a mosaic coming up"},{"time":766121,"text":"and creating this world in their backyards"},{"time":767622,"text":"and in their kitchens."},{"time":769130,"text":"And that's the world I really want to live in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771696,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773080,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}